<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Gary Thompson</span></strong> is an attorney who represents pro bono detainees imprisoned at Guant&aacute;namo Bay. He is also an avid runner and ran the Chicago marathon last October in three hours and thirty-eight minutes &mdash; his personal best. He lives with his wife and children in Washington, D.C.</p><a href="/contributors/gary-thompson" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

